Firestore collection: /bv_phuong_chau/{orgId}/snapshot_bao_cao/{id_snapshot}
Document fields: - ma_bao_cao, ky_bao_cao, phien_ban_chi_so - du_lieu (JSON chunked nếu > 900KB) - chu_ky: { email, ho_ten, vai_tro, thoi_diem, chu_ky_so? } - hash_du_lieu, trang_thai - created_at, updated_at
Firestore rules: - read: vai_tro in ['ADMIN','AUDITOR','OPERATOR','REVIEWER'] - write: vai_tro in ['ADMIN','AUDITOR'] - delete: vai_tro = 'ADMIN' AND document.trang_thai != 'da_chot'
